      <title>通用磨坊因价格上涨而季度销售额降幅小于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/general-mills-posts-smaller-than-expected-drop-quarterly-sales-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦片麦片制造商通用磨坊 (General Mills) 周三公布的季度销售额降幅小于预期，原因是其早餐麦片、零食棒和宠物食品价格上涨，有助于缓解需求放缓带来的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/general-mills-posts-smaller-than-expected-drop-quarterly-sales-2024-03-20/</guid>
